{"id":61246,"date":"2021-07-15T09:04:30","date_gmt":"2021-07-15T08:04:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=61246"},"modified":"2021-11-17T15:24:17","modified_gmt":"2021-11-17T14:24:17","slug":"aubeterre-sur-dronne","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/aubeterre-sur-dronne\/","title":{"rendered":"Aubeterre-sur-Dronne: A Stunning Village in France"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-wander-the-beautiful-streets\"><strong>Wander the Beautiful Streets<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The steep winding streets of Aubeterre-sur-Dronne are like a picture from a holiday postcard. Many of the old stone houses have wooden balconies, complete with colorful hanging flowers; this really adds to the beauty and charm of the town. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165404\/Aubeterre2.jpg\" alt=\"Aubeterre france street\"><\/noscript><img width=\"267\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Aubeterre france street\" class=\"wp-image-61425 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1517px) 100vw, 1517px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165404\/Aubeterre2.jpg 1517w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165404\/Aubeterre2-474x600.jpg 474w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165404\/Aubeterre2-640x810.jpg 640w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165404\/Aubeterre2-267x338.jpg 267w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165404\/Aubeterre2-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165404\/Aubeterre2-129x163.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\