shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>See where <a href=\"#hotels\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">we spend the night, a nomad tent<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Aubeterre france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Aubeterre france\" data-id=\"61488\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=61488\" class=\"wp-image-61488 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195157\/Aubeterre20-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/u