oad\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-600x400.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165754\/Aubeterre13.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-discover-the-underground-church\">Discover the <strong>Underground Church<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Aubeterre-sur-Dronne was once a very important site for pilgrims who would stop in the town on their way to Santiago de Compestela in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spain<\/a>. An important part of this history is the huge underground Monolithic church that still exists here. The Saint-Jean church is the largest underground church in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Europe<\/a> and its size is mind-blowing; it&#x2019;s carved out of the rock to a depth of 20m! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1.jpg\" alt=\"Aubeterre france underground church\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Aubeterre france underground church\" class=\"wp-image-61423 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/12165351\/Aubeterre1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#x2019;re inside, find the staircase that&#x2019;s chiseled into the stone wall and climb 18m up to the viewing gallery. Here, you can gain a great perspective of the work that would have gone into creating this magical church.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entry fee:<\/strong> 6 EUR &#x2013; <strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Opening times: <\/strong>Every day from 9.30 AM &#x2013; 6 PM (closed for lunch 12.30 &#x2013; 2)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/61246&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14201927\/Aubeterre-sur-Dronne-france1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14201927\/Aubeterre-sur-Dronne-france1-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14201927\/Aubeterre-sur-Dronne-france1-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Aubeterre-sur-Dronne: A Stunning Village in France\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-chateau-de-chalais\"><strong>Chateau de Chalais<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Just a 15-minute drive from Aubeterre is the white stone castle &#x2018;<a href=\"http:\/\/www.chateaudechalais.fr\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Chateau de Chalais<\/a>&#x2019;. The fairytale-like building is open to the public and you can take a guided tour around the rooms (many of which have been preserved with their original features). <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Cross the drawbridge to enter the castle &#x2013; a unique part of the castle&#x2019;s history.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14163913\/Aubeterre9-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Aubeterre castle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Aubeterre castle\" data-id=\"61453\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14163913\/Aubeterre9.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=61453\" class=\"wp-image-61453 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14163913\/Aubeterre9-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14163913\/Aubeterre9-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14163913\/Aubeterre9-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14163913