Rent a car locally through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a> as they work with local car rental companies. When booking through Sunny Cars, all insurances are included, no surprises when collecting your car. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your local rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/bordeaux\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Bordeaux<\/a> is the nearest airport and is about an hour&#x2019;s drive away.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/paris-city-trip-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to spend a weekend in Paris!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14171811\/Aubeterre16.jpg\" alt=\"Aubeterre france village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Aubeterre france village\" class=\"wp-image-61471 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14171811\/Aubeterre16.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14171811\/Aubeterre16-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/