nized tours leaving from Aubeterre to the surrounding sights and there are public buses leaving from the town too. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14.jpg\" alt=\"Aubeterre\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Aubeterre\" class=\"wp-image-61465 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14165809\/Aubeterre14.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-best-time-to-visit-aubeterre\"><strong>Best time to visit Aubeterre<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit Aubeterre in the spring or summer months when everything is green, luscious, and there are beautiful sunny days. This is also a great time to enjoy the watersports and to take the opportunity to camp and get out into nature.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-where-to-eat-in-aubeterre\"><strong>Where to eat in Aubeterre<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite the town&#x2019;s small size it offers a lot of fantastic restaurants! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>La Taverne Pierre V&#xE9;ry (French)<\/li><li>La Tapazzeria (Pizzaria)<\/li><li>Le Garage (burgers)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195125\/Aubeterre18-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Aubeterre france cafe\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Aubeterre france cafe\" data-id=\"61482\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/14195125\/Aubeterre18.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=61482\" class=\"wp-image-61482 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\"